Job Description
My Client who is an international feeder carrier, operating in over 140 ports worldwide, is in search of a Ship Planner in Dubai.
You will have previous experience in a similar role with a feeder/container ship company. You will be responsible for stowage planning, ensuring vessel loading are maximised, cost control of terminals, operations and bunker consumption. You must have excellent communication skills as you will be liaising with Line Managers, terminals, agents etc
You must already have eligibility to work in UAE. Ex-seafarers with container ship experience may also apply
Qualifications
Bachelors Degree or equivalent
